77
00:03:40,460 --> 00:03:41,300
Why should I?

78
00:03:42,540 --> 00:03:43,540
Where were you when others

79
00:03:43,540 --> 00:03:44,380
called me a monster?

80
00:03:45,700 --> 00:03:46,980
Where were you when they said

81
00:03:46,980 --> 00:03:48,020
I had no father?

82
00:03:48,380 --> 00:03:49,420
And now you suddenly show up,

83
00:03:49,420 --> 00:03:50,620
wanting me to call you "Father"?

84
00:03:52,500 --> 00:03:53,420
Why?

85
00:03:56,020 --> 00:03:56,860
Yingdan,

86
00:03:57,740 --> 00:03:59,500
he just explained everything.

87
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:00,580
I don't accept that.

88
00:04:01,900 --> 00:04:02,780
Yingdan,

89
00:04:02,780 --> 00:04:04,340
just now, your father said

90
00:04:04,540 --> 00:04:05,620
he didn't know

91
00:04:05,620 --> 00:04:07,820
the two of us were still alive.

92
00:04:08,900 --> 00:04:10,780
