99
00:04:25,060 --> 00:04:26,620
Having you protect her

100
00:04:26,620 --> 00:04:28,060
puts me at ease.

101
00:04:29,140 --> 00:04:29,980
Yingdan,

102
00:04:30,540 --> 00:04:32,220
when you're feeling better,

103
00:04:32,940 --> 00:04:34,340
I'd like to draw some of your blood

104
00:04:35,020 --> 00:04:36,220
to study it closely.

105
00:04:37,180 --> 00:04:39,180
I want to create a new antidote

106
00:04:39,380 --> 00:04:41,940
so you won't suffer
the backlash anymore.

107
00:04:44,380 --> 00:04:45,220
Liu Guang,

108
00:04:46,820 --> 00:04:48,140
as the Demonic Sect's leader,

109
00:04:48,300 --> 00:04:49,700
you must return to Huizhou with me.

110
00:04:50,380 --> 00:04:51,300
Deng Yunfeng,

111
00:04:52,140 --> 00:04:53,620
didn't you hear?

112
00:04:53,820 --> 00:04:54,660
They were

113
00:04:54,860 --> 00:04:56,460
falsely accused back then.

114
00:04:56,660 --> 00:04:57,980
You're so naive.

115
00:04:58,660 --> 00:05:00,140
You believe whatever he says?

116
00:05:00,140 --> 00:05:01,580
I deal in evidence.

117
00:05:03,820 --> 00:05:04,660
Lord Deng,

118
00:05:05,100 --> 00:05:05,940
he's my husband.

119
00:05:05,940 --> 00:05:06,940
I know him.

120
00:05:07,580 --> 00:05:09,540
He's made many mistakes,

121
00:05:09,780 --> 00:05:12,100
but he's not an unforgivable villain.

122
00:05:13,780 --> 00:05:15,180
Now that he's returned,

123
00:05:15,460 --> 00:05:16,300
he'll be

124
00:05:16,780 --> 00:05:18,700
a good husband

125
00:05:20,420 --> 00:05:21,740
and a good father to Yingdan.

126
00:05:25,580 --> 00:05:26,420
Yunfeng,

127
00:05:28,260 --> 00:05:29,780
for my sake, I beg you.

128
00:05:30,700 --> 00:05:31,540
Liu Guang,

129
00:05:33,300 --> 00:05:35,740
I hope you'll fulfill your duty
as a father

130
00:05:37,420 --> 00:05:39,020
and develop the antidote soon.

131
00:05:42,060 --> 00:05:44,620
Yingdan is my own daughter.

132
00:05:51,420 --> 00:05:52,260
Also,

133
00:05:53,580 --> 00:05:54,980
Gou Lingfeng, you have to agree

134
00:05:55,420 --> 00:05:56,500
to cooperate with me once we leave.

135
00:05:57,980 --> 00:05:59,820
I already promised Aunt Lan.

136
00:06:00,220 --> 00:06:02,420
I'm staying in Poison Valley

137
00:06:02,700 --> 00:06:03,740
to be with Yingdan.

138
00:06:07,220 --> 00:06:08,060
Lingfeng,

139
00:06:08,460 --> 00:06:09,980
