140
00:06:09,980 --> 00:06:11,740
don't you have any ambition?

141
00:06:12,420 --> 00:06:14,060
If you've got no drive at all,

142
00:06:14,060 --> 00:06:15,340
how can I feel secure

143
00:06:15,340 --> 00:06:16,860
marrying my daughter off to you?

144
00:06:17,340 --> 00:06:18,460
- Mom!
- Wait,

145
00:06:18,460 --> 00:06:20,940
Aunt Lan, that's not
what you said before!

146
00:06:21,140 --> 00:06:22,900
You said I didn't need to

147
00:06:23,100 --> 00:06:24,420
worry about a career,

148
00:06:24,660 --> 00:06:27,580
that I could just pick flowers
and chill,

149
00:06:27,580 --> 00:06:29,260
and not try to

150
00:06:29,260 --> 00:06:31,540
have my nice cake and eat it too!

151
00:06:31,540 --> 00:06:33,060
- That was...
- Enough.

152
00:06:33,340 --> 00:06:34,180
Master,

153
00:06:34,660 --> 00:06:35,660
maybe read a book or two.

154
00:06:36,580 --> 00:06:37,420
I...

155
00:06:37,820 --> 00:06:39,340
That was before.

156
00:06:39,900 --> 00:06:41,420
Times have changed.

157
00:06:41,860 --> 00:06:42,860
Now,

158
00:06:42,860 --> 00:06:44,500
I think a man with ambition

159
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:45,540
is very important.

160
00:06:47,300 --> 00:06:48,860
So cooperate nicely

161
00:06:48,860 --> 00:06:49,860
with Lord Deng.

162
00:06:53,020 --> 00:06:54,100
Cooperate with him.

163
00:06:56,860 --> 00:06:57,740
Alright then.

164
00:06:58,940 --> 00:07:00,020
You better keep your word.

165
00:07:11,660 --> 00:07:14,620
(Poison Valley)

166
00:07:15,420 --> 00:07:16,380
Mom,

167
00:07:16,380 --> 00:07:18,140
