to stay with you?

168
00:07:19,300 --> 00:07:20,140
Aunt Lan,

169
00:07:20,780 --> 00:07:22,900
you really aren't coming with us?

170
00:07:24,660 --> 00:07:25,620
I'm not going.

171
00:07:26,540 --> 00:07:28,380
The poison in me has been cured.

172
00:07:28,380 --> 00:07:30,460
Even without the miasma, I'll be fine.

173
00:07:30,460 --> 00:07:31,300
Besides,

174
00:07:31,740 --> 00:07:33,140
I'm used to living here now.

175
00:07:33,140 --> 00:07:34,060
No point in moving around.

176
00:07:35,060 --> 00:07:36,220
Most importantly,

177
00:07:37,340 --> 00:07:38,340
wherever Guang is,

178
00:07:39,060 --> 00:07:39,900
that's where I'll be.

179
00:07:40,100 --> 00:07:41,260
Even though I really want

180
00:07:41,260 --> 00:07:43,140
to stay here and live out
my days with you,

181
00:07:43,340 --> 00:07:44,180
for the sake

182
00:07:44,540 --> 00:07:45,980
of our daughter's poison,

183
00:07:46,300 --> 00:07:48,340
I need to develop the antidote.

184
00:07:51,100 --> 00:07:51,940
Yingdan,

185
00:07:52,460 --> 00:07:54,700
you must be very careful out there.

186
00:07:56,540 --> 00:07:57,380
Lingfeng,

187
00:07:57,980 --> 00:07:59,940
you better not mistreat Yingdan.

188
00:08:00,340 --> 00:08:01,540
Aunt Lan, don't worry.

189
00:08:01,540 --> 00:08:02,500
With me around,

190
00:08:02,500 --> 00:08:04,780
Yingdan won't suffer even a scratch.

191
00:08:05,260 --> 00:08:06,940
And I've brought
the blood-replenishing pills

192
00:08:06,940 --> 00:08:08,060
you gave me.

193
00:08:08,260 --> 00:08:09,340
Her backlash

194
00:08:09,340 --> 00:08:10,900
shouldn't be a problem.

195
00:08:10,900 --> 00:08:11,820
Everyone,

196
00:08:11,820 --> 00:08:13,060
I'll take my leave now.

197
00:08:13,060 --> 00:08:14,060
Until we meet again.

198
00:08:15,340 --> 00:08:16,180
Linglan,

199
00:08:17,100 --> 00:08:18,020
I have to go.

200
00:08:18,420 --> 00:08:19,300
Wait for me at home.

201
00:08:20,700 --> 00:08:22,140
I'll be waiting for you, Guang.

202
00:08:22,140 --> 00:08:22,980
Alright.

203
00:08:29,580 --> 00:08:31,380
Mom, we're heading off too.

204
00:08:32,740 --> 00:08:34,060
Go on, go on.

205
00:08:35,140 --> 00:08:36,260
All of you, go.

206
00:08:36,260 --> 00:08:37,300
Just go!

207
00:08:40,740 --> 00:08:41,860
Take care of yourselves!

208
00:08:41,860 --> 00:08:43,500
I missed you so much, Yingdan.

209
00:08:43,500 --> 00:08:44,340
- I just...
- From now on, you two

210
00:08:44,340 --> 00:08:45,340
