212
00:08:46,220 --> 00:08:48,100
You two are a lot worse than us.

213
00:08:48,580 --> 00:08:50,020
- Are we?
- Are we?

214
00:08:50,020 --> 00:08:50,860
Yes.

215
00:08:52,740 --> 00:08:53,580
