218
00:09:00,140 --> 00:09:00,980
Whatever.

219
00:09:01,340 --> 00:09:02,300
Figure it out myself.

220
00:09:03,260 --> 00:09:04,460
That's a problem.

221
00:09:04,900 --> 00:09:05,740
Not at all.

222
00:09:06,780 --> 00:09:08,140
(Poison Valley)

223
00:09:14,780 --> 00:09:15,820
Vice Chairman,

224
00:09:15,820 --> 00:09:17,060
what should we do?

225
00:09:17,380 --> 00:09:19,940
The Demonic Sect's leader Liu Guang
has reappeared,

226
00:09:19,940 --> 00:09:21,300
and we just came back like this.

227
00:09:21,300 --> 00:09:22,500
That doesn't sit right.

228
00:09:23,900 --> 00:09:26,420
We took heavy losses in Poison Valley.

229
00:09:27,060 --> 00:09:28,140
What were we supposed to do?

230
00:09:28,500 --> 00:09:29,580
Stay and die?

231
00:09:31,500 --> 00:09:33,100
This is a major issue.

232
00:09:33,100 --> 00:09:34,700
I'll report it to the Chairman

233
00:09:34,700 --> 00:09:35,900
and await his decision.

234
00:09:37,620 --> 00:09:38,820
And you!

235
00:09:39,740 --> 00:09:40,820
You made me so mad.

236
00:09:40,820 --> 00:09:42,220
What kind of people did you find?

237
00:09:42,900 --> 00:09:44,460
They didn't follow a single order!

238
00:09:44,460 --> 00:09:45,940
Most of the MAA's heroes

239
00:09:45,940 --> 00:09:47,100
are on missions.

240
00:09:47,100 --> 00:09:48,300
