charging at Poison Valley.

256
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,020
Deng Yunfeng

257
00:10:29,020 --> 00:10:31,180
tried to stop them
in his godfather's name,

258
00:10:31,180 --> 00:10:32,020
but no one cared.

259
00:10:32,030 --> 00:10:32,910
It didn't work at all.

260
00:10:33,020 --> 00:10:33,860
And then?

261
00:10:34,100 --> 00:10:34,940
Then...

262
00:10:37,100 --> 00:10:38,140
Then I ran.

263
00:10:38,340 --> 00:10:39,220
You ran?

264
00:10:39,860 --> 00:10:40,700
My Lady,

265
00:10:41,100 --> 00:10:42,060
Gou Lingfeng and his crew

266
00:10:42,060 --> 00:10:43,700
probably didn't make it out.

267
00:10:44,060 --> 00:10:44,980
And

268
00:10:44,980 --> 00:10:47,060
Deng Yunfeng won't let this go easily.

269
00:10:47,060 --> 00:10:48,540
It's way too embarrassing.

270
00:10:49,620 --> 00:10:51,340
I didn't expect things

271
00:10:51,340 --> 00:10:52,660
to spiral this badly.

272
00:10:53,180 --> 00:10:54,980
But I told you before,

273
00:10:54,980 --> 00:10:56,540
someone was bound to lose patience.

274
00:10:57,060 --> 00:10:58,500
I just didn't think it'd be him.

275
00:10:59,060 --> 00:11:00,300
He actually rescued

276
00:11:00,540 --> 00:11:02,580
Gou Lingfeng and the others.

277
00:11:03,180 --> 00:11:05,140
