00:20:56,940 --> 00:20:58,620
gave me everything.

561
00:20:59,490 --> 00:21:00,900
Then we have nothing to talk about.

562
00:21:01,500 --> 00:21:02,780
What is wrong with you?

563
00:21:05,620 --> 00:21:07,500
You got brainwashed by that old fox

564
00:21:07,500 --> 00:21:08,460
Wu Guangming again?

565
00:21:08,660 --> 00:21:09,780
Deng Yunfeng!

566
00:21:09,780 --> 00:21:11,180
Watch your tongue!

567
00:21:11,660 --> 00:21:14,020
Chairman Wu has the heart
of a true leader.

568
00:21:14,030 --> 00:21:14,980
Only he

569
00:21:15,100 --> 00:21:17,820
can guide the martial world
in the right direction.

570
00:21:18,340 --> 00:21:19,180
I

571
00:21:19,180 --> 00:21:21,060
can tell right from wrong.

572
00:21:21,620 --> 00:21:22,940
You think you can?

573
00:21:23,980 --> 00:21:25,620
Wu Guangming is a hypocrite!

574
00:21:25,620 --> 00:21:26,940
Only you still believe him,

575
00:21:27,460 --> 00:21:29,500
like a big fool!

576
00:21:30,020 --> 00:21:31,060
The dumbest thing I did

577
00:21:31,060 --> 00:21:32,700
was believing your lies

578
00:21:32,980 --> 00:21:34,580
and agreeing to work with you.

579
00:21:34,580 --> 00:21:35,740
Enough! Quit arguing.

580
00:21:36,700 --> 00:21:37,780
Is it really impossible

581
00:21:38,340 --> 00:21:40,700
for us to build
a brand new martial world

582
00:21:40,700 --> 00:21:41,660
without Eunuch Deng

583
00:21:41,660 --> 00:21:42,860
or Wu Guangming?

584
00:21:47,700 --> 00:21:48,940
- Impossible!
- Impossible!

585
00:21:53,940 --> 00:21:56,940
(Paper Shop)

586
00:22:01,300 --> 00:22:02,140
Wait.

587
00:22:03,620 --> 00:22:04,500
Who are you?

588
00:22:04,660 --> 00:22:05,620
I've never seen you around.

589
00:22:07,100 --> 00:22:07,940
Young man,

590
00:22:08,180 --> 00:22:09,140
who are you?

591
00:22:09,580 --> 00:22:10,420
I...

592
00:22:11,220 --> 00:22:12,060
Uncle Wang.

593
00:22:13,260 --> 00:22:14,100
Chief!

594
00:22:15,180 --> 00:22:16,140
The Chief has returned!

595
00:22:16,140 --> 00:22:17,140
Wang!

596
00:22:17,420 --> 00:22:18,260
Chief!

597
00:22:18,620 --> 00:22:19,540
You're alive!

598
00:22:19,540 --> 00:22:21,140
Where have you been all these years?

599
00:22:21,140 --> 00:22:22,020
Yes, Chief,

600
00:22:22,020 --> 00:22:23,100
you're finally back!

601
00:22:23,100 --> 00:22:23,940
Wang,

602
00:22:24,500 --> 00:22:26,300
have you all been well these years?

603
00:22:26,900 --> 00:22:29,100
We've suffered bitterly.

604
00:22:29,540 --> 00:22:30,460
- Yes.
- The MAA

605
00:22:30,460 --> 00:22:32,220
wants to wipe us out completely.

606
00:22:32,380 --> 00:22:34,140
We barely survive now.

607
00:22:34,140 --> 00:22:34,980
That's right.

608
00:22:34,980 --> 00:22:36,220
Brothers, friends,

609
00:22:37,020 --> 00:22:38,340
I know it's been hard

610
00:22:38,340 --> 00:22:39,460
over the past years.

611
00:22:40,420 --> 00:22:41,260
But now,

612
00:22:41,660 --> 00:22:43,460
our Divine Sect is rising again.

613
00:22:44,020 --> 00:22:45,900
I need your full support.

614
00:22:46,900 --> 00:22:48,700
My lord, a message from Eunuch Deng.

615
00:22:55,420 --> 00:22:56,540
Tell our men to prepare.

616
00:22:57,140 --> 00:22:58,460
We've got a mission.

617
00:22:59,100 --> 00:22:59,940
Yes.

618
00:23:00,700 --> 00:23:01,540
Changzai,

619
00:23:01,820 --> 00:23:03,380
the Hero Gathering is upon us.

620
00:23:03,940 --> 00:23:06,060
Not a single mistake can be allowed.

621
00:23:07,220 --> 00:23:09,780
Gou Lingfeng must win the Hero Token.

622
00:23:10,660 --> 00:23:12,900
Only then can we restrain Eunuch Deng.

623
00:23:13,580 --> 00:23:15,140
But the biggest problem now

624
00:23:15,340 --> 00:23:17,220
is that he can't use demonic powers.

625
00:23:17,420 --> 00:23:18,980
Don't worry about that, Chairman.

626
00:23:18,980 --> 00:23:20,380
The current participants

627
00:23:20,380 --> 00:23:22,060
are all from within the MAA.

628
00:23:23,140 --> 00:23:25,380
I'll make sure everything is handled.

629
00:23:27,020 --> 00:23:27,940
As long as Gou Lingfeng

630
00:23:27,940 --> 00:23:29,900
makes it to the finals,

631
00:23:31,060 --> 00:23:33,140
I'll hand over my position
as Chairman to him.

632
00:23:34,260 --> 00:23:35,820
After ten years in this role,

633
00:23:36,300 --> 00:23:37,380
I'm tired.

634
00:23:38,820 --> 00:23:39,900
The future of the martial world

635
00:23:39,900 --> 00:23:41,620
belongs to the young.

636
00:23:44,540 --> 00:23:45,420
Changzai,

637
00:23:46,780 --> 00:23:48,380
aside from me,

638
00:23:48,380 --> 00:23:50,140
you're the most senior in the MAA.

639
00:23:50,500 --> 00:23:51,780
You have no objections

640
00:23:52,220 --> 00:23:53,660
to this arrangement, do you?

641
00:23:55,660 --> 00:23:56,500
Well,

642
00:23:57,180 --> 00:23:58,020
Chairman,

643
00:23:58,860 --> 00:24:00,140
how could I?

644
00:24:00,690 --> 00:24:01,700
You've dedicated yourself

645
00:24:02,500 --> 00:24:04,100
to the growth of the MAA
all these years.

646
00:24:05,540 --> 00:24:07,180
I will handle everything personally

647
00:24:08,420 --> 00:24:09,540
so you have no need to worry.

648
00:24:12,260 --> 00:24:16,900
(Eliminate Evil and Uphold Justice)

649
00:24:16,900 --> 00:24:18,940
We thank Eunuch Deng for taking time
to join us.

650
00:24:20,140 --> 00:24:22,820
My continued tenure as Chairman
of the MAA

651
00:24:23,140 --> 00:24:24,820
is entirely thanks to the trust

652
00:24:24,820 --> 00:24:26,300
from the court and from you.

653
00:24:27,780 --> 00:24:30,340
Chairman Wu, you're far too modest.

654
00:24:30,540 --> 00:24:32,620
You're not only a martial master,

655
00:24:32,620 --> 00:24:34,340
but also a capable leader.

656
00:24:34,340 --> 00:24:35,420
Under your guidance

657
00:24:35,420 --> 00:24:36,740
all these years,

658
00:24:36,940 --> 00:24:39,340
the MAA has grown ever stronger.

659
00:24:40,900 --> 00:24:41,980
At times,

660
00:24:41,980 --> 00:24:43,860
I even worry,

661
00:24:43,860 --> 00:24:45,180
what would

662
00:24:45,180 --> 00:24:48,420
become of the MAA

663
00:24:48,940 --> 00:24:50,580
if one day we lost you?

664
00:24:52,460 --> 00:24:54,740
What's that supposed to mean?

665
00:25:00,180 --> 00:25:02,140
You flatter me.

666
00:25:02,500 --> 00:25:04,140
As long as the court needs me,

667
00:25:04,740 --> 00:25:07,060
I will devote myself

668
00:25:07,060 --> 00:25:08,340
to the MAA

669
00:25:08,540 --> 00:25:09,740
unto death.

670
00:25:11,140 --> 00:25:11,980
By the way,

671
00:25:12,820 --> 00:25:14,740
He Changzai is the lead coordinator

672
00:25:14,740 --> 00:25:15,860
of this year's Hero Gathering.

673
00:25:16,180 --> 00:25:17,020
Changzai,

674
00:25:17,580 --> 00:25:19,100
present the full schedule

675
00:25:19,100 --> 00:25:21,220
to Eunuch Deng in detail.

676
00:25:21,980 --> 00:25:22,820
Yes, Chairman.

677
00:25:26,380 --> 00:25:27,220
Sir.

678
00:25:44,180 --> 00:25:46,500
Vice Chairman of the MAA, He Changzai,

679
00:25:47,220 --> 00:25:48,540
is guilty of embezzlement

680
00:25:48,820 --> 00:25:49,980
and abuse of power.

681
00:25:49,980 --> 00:25:51,540
The evidence is solid.

682
00:25:51,540 --> 00:25:53,660
I'm placing you under arrest.

683
00:25:54,660 --> 00:25:56,500
- For real?
- How is that possible?

684
00:26:05,140 --> 00:26:05,980
Deng Yunfeng,

685
00:26:06,380 --> 00:26:08,540
Even if Eunuch Deng is here,

686
00:26:09,300 --> 00:26:11,780
you can't slander someone like this
in public!

687
00:26:12,740 --> 00:26:13,740
Inspector Deng,

688
00:26:15,340 --> 00:26:17,980
you accuse Vice Chairman He
of corruption,

689
00:26:18,700 --> 00:26:19,740
do you have proof?

690
00:26:20,580 --> 00:26:22,700
If you can't substantiate it,

691
00:26:23,740 --> 00:26:25,300
then it's defamation.

692
00:26:27,900 --> 00:26:29,020
Forgive me, Chairman.

693
00:26:29,660 --> 00:26:31,820
But He Changzai is despicable.

694
00:26:32,460 --> 00:26:33,660
He's fooled

695
00:26:33,660 --> 00:26:34,740
not only the public,

696
00:26:34,740 --> 00:26:37,420
but even you, sir.

697
00:26:38,780 --> 00:26:40,140
I've confirmed the following:

698
00:26:40,420 --> 00:26:42,740
He owns six private residences,

699
00:26:42,740 --> 00:26:44,020
eight estates,

700
00:26:44,020 --> 00:26:45,420
a hundred servants,

701
00:26:45,420 --> 00:26:46,860
over a hundred acres of farmland.

702
00:26:46,860 --> 00:26:48,620
- That much?
- What?

703
00:26:48,620 --> 00:26:49,940
- I...
- I wonder

704
00:26:49,940 --> 00:26:52,860
if you have that kind of wealth,
Chairman?

705
00:26:56,180 --> 00:26:57,020
Deng Yunfeng, you...

706
00:26:57,020 --> 00:26:58,060
And these

707
00:26:59,780 --> 00:27:02,820
are account books
from the Juhong Pavilion.

708
00:27:03,220 --> 00:27:05,300
He receives a hefty sum monthly

709
00:27:05,300 --> 00:27:06,780
from them.

710
00:27:07,340 --> 00:27:08,460
Also, silver from the

711
00:27:08,460 --> 00:27:09,860
Zang Family Trade Association.

712
00:27:09,860 --> 00:27:10,900
And this,

713
00:27:11,180 --> 00:27:14,340
a signed IOU from Gou Lingfeng of GFTA.

714
00:27:15,100 --> 00:27:16,060
Vice Chairman He,

715
00:27:16,340 --> 00:27:17,260
how

716
00:27:17,500 --> 00:27:18,980
do you explain these?

717
00:27:21,180 --> 00:27:22,020
Chairman,

718
00:27:23,060 --> 00:27:24,660
I've been framed!

719
00:27:29,620 --> 00:27:31,620
Please judge justly!

720
00:27:38,980 --> 00:27:40,900
This is the MAA's matter!

721
00:27:41,070 --> 00:27:42,260
Why are they interfering?

722
00:27:42,260 --> 00:27:45,980
(Martial)

723
00:27:45,980 --> 00:27:49,100
The MAA has always been just.

724
00:27:51,100 --> 00:27:52,820
We will not let a single wrongdoer
escape,

725
00:27:53,660 --> 00:27:55,660
nor will we wrong a single good man.

726
00:28:03,620 --> 00:28:04,460
Guards!

727
00:28:05,300 --> 00:28:07,660
Take He Changzai to the prison.

728
00:28:08,940 --> 00:28:09,780
Chairman!

729
00:28:10,300 --> 00:28:12,060
After the Hero Gathering,

730
00:28:12,540 --> 00:28:14,100
I will personally see this case

731
00:28:14,100 --> 00:28:16,020
thoroughly investigated.

732
00:28:16,940 --> 00:28:18,100
Wise decision, Chairman!

733
00:28:20,380 --> 00:28:21,220
Changzai!

734
00:28:21,220 --> 00:28:27,100
(Eliminate Evil and Uphold Justice)

735
00:28:31,060 --> 00:28:34,300
Chairman Wu is truly fair and upright!

736
00:28:34,300 --> 00:28:36,700
I admire you.

737
00:28:36,940 --> 00:28:38,180
You are the true treasure

738
00:28:38,180 --> 00:28:41,860
of the MAA.

739
00:28:44,940 --> 00:28:46,100
Although He Changzai

740
00:28:46,620 --> 00:28:48,460
has been a longtime subordinate,

741
00:28:49,180 --> 00:28:50,980
but since there are accusations,

742
00:28:51,420 --> 00:28:53,540
the MAA will not tolerate it.

743
00:28:53,860 --> 00:28:55,540
We will get to the bottom of it.

744
00:28:55,540 --> 00:28:56,500
Very well.

745
00:28:57,340 --> 00:28:59,100
An imperial decree!

746
00:29:09,460 --> 00:29:10,740
By the mandate of Heaven,

747
00:29:10,740 --> 00:29:12,220
His Majesty decrees:

748
00:29:12,220 --> 00:29:16,300
The MAA is central to the martial world
of Great Xia.

749
00:29:16,300 --> 00:29:18,780
(Imperial Edict)
To ensure vitality

750
00:29:18,780 --> 00:29:19,900
and growth,

751
00:29:19,900 --> 00:29:21,300
it is hereby ordered:

752
00:29:21,300 --> 00:29:22,780
The presidency of the MAA

753
00:29:22,780 --> 00:29:25,060
may not exceed two consecutive terms.

754
00:29:28,660 --> 00:29:30,060
Thus decreed.

755
00:29:31,580 --> 00:29:36,180
Long live His Majesty!

756
00:29:36,540 --> 00:29:37,900
Everyone, rise.

757
00:29:42,100 --> 00:29:43,140
Guangming,

758
00:29:44,260 --> 00:29:46,300
this is all His Majesty's will.

759
00:29:48,860 --> 00:29:50,540
Are they targeting Chairman Wu?

760
00:29:50,540 --> 00:29:52,220
- Exactly!
- It's clearly aimed at him!

761
00:29:52,620 --> 00:29:53,740
You're obviously

762
00:29:53,740 --> 00:29:55,260
targeting Chairman Wu!

763
00:29:55,260 --> 00:29:56,100
Master!

764
00:29:56,300 --> 00:29:57,660
Are all young people

765
00:29:57,660 --> 00:29:59,340
so disrespectful now?

766
00:29:59,340 --> 00:30:02,420
The MAA was founded by Chairman Wu.

767
00:30:02,660 --> 00:30:04,540
We've all seen his dedication

768
00:30:04,540 --> 00:30:05,900
to the MAA.

769
00:30:05,900 --> 00:30:08,140
And from the beginning,

770
00:30:08,140 --> 00:30:10,100
he's been our one and only Chairman.

771
00:30:10,620 --> 00:30:12,260
You dare say this imperial decree

772
00:30:12,260 --> 00:30:13,980
isn't aimed at him?

773
00:30:13,980 --> 00:30:15,980
Then what do you intend to do?

774
00:30:15,980 --> 00:30:17,540
Defy the imperial edict?

775
00:30:17,540 --> 00:30:18,500
And what if I do?

776
00:30:18,900 --> 00:30:19,740
Lingfeng.

777
00:30:24,980 --> 00:30:26,020
Gou Lingfeng.

778
00:30:26,220 --> 00:30:27,620
It's been a while.

779
00:30:28,500 --> 00:30:29,940
Seems I forgot something.

780
00:30:30,140 --> 00:30:31,020
Chairman Wu,

781
00:30:31,020 --> 00:30:32,940
the MAA represents the righteous path

782
00:30:32,940 --> 00:30:35,140
of the martial world,

783
00:30:35,140 --> 00:30:35,980
right?

784
00:30:36,300 --> 00:30:38,380
If you let a demonic art user

785
00:30:38,380 --> 00:30:40,260
- You...
- participate in the Hero Gathering,

786
00:30:40,420 --> 00:30:41,460
what would people say?

787
00:30:41,460 --> 00:30:43,100
Wouldn't the whole martial world

788
00:30:43,100 --> 00:30:45,900
laugh at you for having
no decent talent?

789
00:30:45,900 --> 00:30:47,460
Eunuch Deng, that's unjust.

790
00:30:47,820 --> 00:30:49,380
The matter of demonic techniques

791
00:30:49,380 --> 00:30:50,780
was clarified long ago.

792
00:30:50,780 --> 00:30:52,460
He only learned a few moves

793
00:30:52,460 --> 00:30:55,260
to infiltrate the Demonic Sect as a spy.

794
00:30:55,260 --> 00:30:56,580
So just because he says so, it's true?

795
00:30:57,220 --> 00:30:58,660
To me, he looks

796
00:30:58,660 --> 00:31:00,340
more like a spy the Demonic Cult

797
00:31:00,340 --> 00:31:02,940
planted in the MAA!

798
00:31:02,940 --> 00:31:03,940
You...

799
00:31:03,940 --> 00:31:06,740
Gou Lingfeng possesses demonic powers,

800
00:31:06,740 --> 00:31:09,940
and now he's yelling
in front of everyone,

801
00:31:09,940 --> 00:31:11,420
shaming the court.

802
00:31:11,420 --> 00:31:14,300
I say, disqualify him from...

803
00:31:14,300 --> 00:31:15,260
Bah!

804
00:31:15,820 --> 00:31:17,060
Spitting at authority,

805
00:31:17,060 --> 00:31:18,340
disrespecting the court!

806
00:31:18,660 --> 00:31:19,540
Please calm your anger.

807
00:31:19,540 --> 00:31:20,740
He didn't mean it that way.

808
00:31:21,260 --> 00:31:22,140
Lingfeng!

809
00:31:22,140 --> 00:31:23,460
Apologize now!

810
00:31:23,460 --> 00:31:25,700
- I...
- You learned demonic arts

811
00:31:25,700 --> 00:31:26,660
to protect yourself,

812
00:31:26,660 --> 00:31:27,500
didn't you?

813
00:31:27,500 --> 00:31:29,300
Then making a scene like this

814
00:31:29,540 --> 00:31:31,140
just makes you look guilty.

815
00:31:31,140 --> 00:31:32,820
It proves your crime.

816
00:31:32,820 --> 00:31:33,660
Don't you see?

817
00:31:33,910 --> 00:31:34,760
Come on!

818
00:31:36,060 --> 00:31:36,900
Lingfeng,

819
00:31:37,420 --> 00:31:38,260
apologize!

820
00:31:43,060 --> 00:31:44,140
- Sir,
- Please calm down.

821
00:31:44,140 --> 00:31:45,420
I was wrong.

822
00:31:45,420 --> 00:31:46,300
Yes.

823
00:31:46,300 --> 00:31:47,940
It was rash of me.

824
00:31:48,300 --> 00:31:49,190
I apologize.

825
00:31:49,190 --> 00:31:50,100
Please don't be angry.

826
00:31:50,100 --> 00:31:50,940
Master.

827
00:31:55,500 --> 00:31:56,340
You...

828
00:31:56,540 --> 00:31:58,340
You're cursing me to die!

829
00:31:58,340 --> 00:31:59,220
Wu Guangming!

830
00:31:59,220 --> 00:32:00,500
You're doing this on purpose, right?

831
00:32:00,500 --> 00:32:02,180
No, no!

832
00:32:02,180 --> 00:32:03,100
Get up!

833
00:32:03,100 --> 00:32:04,060
- Stop it now!
- Sir!

834
00:32:04,340 --> 00:32:05,180
No, no, no.

835
00:32:05,500 --> 00:32:06,500
Please don't be angry!

836
00:32:06,500 --> 00:32:08,100
What's wrong, sir?

837
00:32:08,100 --> 00:32:09,540
Lingfeng,

838
00:32:09,780 --> 00:32:12,740
that's a ritual reserved for the dead!

839
00:32:12,740 --> 00:32:14,300
For the dead?

840
00:32:14,900 --> 00:32:16,140
Sir, I...

841
00:32:16,140 --> 00:32:17,620
No one ever taught me that!

842
00:32:17,620 --> 00:32:18,460
I... I was...

843
00:32:19,580 --> 00:32:20,700
How about this?

844
00:32:20,940 --> 00:32:22,820
You do that to me too.

845
00:32:22,820 --> 00:32:23,860
Balance it out.

846
00:32:23,860 --> 00:32:25,020
- What did you say?
